" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Malrotation at surgery",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 447px; height: 297px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    With malrotation, Ladd's bands cross the duodenum, causing extrinsic obstruction. Here the Ladd's bands have been lifted up to expose the duodenum underneath.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
